<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ṣlạty lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ṣlạty lyk ạ̉nyn qlby ḥnyn ạlʿmr llmʿny̱
 wmhmạ ttwh kẖṭạwynạ tʿwd mn tạny tjmʿnạ
 ṣlạty lyk btgẖslny btgẖzl rwḥy twb frḥẗ
 btạkẖd qlby mn ạ̹ydh wtrsm lh ṭryq bkrh
 2- ṣlạty dmʿẗ ʿly̱ bạbk wsẖwq ạlrwḥ lạ̉ʿtạbk
 wạ̹nt ạlạ̉hl wạlṣḥbẗ ḥyạty tmwt fy gẖyạbk
 ṣlạty lyk btsẖfyny tḥrrny wtsbyny
 wymlạ qlby nwr ḥbk yạ mạlk ʿmry wsnyny
 3- ṣlạty lyk dwạ jrwḥy sẖbʿ qlby fy zmạn ạljwʿ
 wlmạ tfyḍ by ậlạmy ạ̹ydk tsẖfy wjʿ rwḥy
 ndy̱ ạlfjryẗ dy ṣlạty yṣḥy ạlrwḥ jwạyạ
 ngẖm ysry fy wjdạny yswd ḥbk ʿly̱ ḥyạty</lyrics>
